&lt;li&gt;Partner with analytical development to define method development, qualification, and validation strategy for drug substance release and stability testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Quality to align drug substance specifications, batch disposition, and GMP compliance across CDMOs, and to support inspection and regulatory submission readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage drug substance post-approval change control strategy for manufacturing changes at CDMOs.&lt;/li&gt;
